    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi. Imperante domno nostro 
                            Lodohvvico magno <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >imperatore</rs>, anno imperi sui septimodecimo, die de mense december,
                        indicione quintadecima. Per anc pagina livelli do adque trado ego <persName
                            ref="#people/1241" key="#Abbots #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis"
                            >Vvarnefrit</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monesterii</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/15"><orgName ref="#juridical_persons/47"
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Petiae #Houses #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Wood #Rent_in_kind #Operae #Exenia #Actionarii/actores #Wine #Minores #Legumes #Maiores #Hay/fodder #Fruits/vegetables #Land_clearing #Monasteries #Abbots"
                            >Nonantolas</orgName></placeName> tibi vero <persName key="#Coloni/tenants #Freeborn"><name
                                ref="Gisbertus">Gixeberto</name></persName> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Angelbertus">Angebert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Freeborn">libero ominem</rs>. ldest rebus illis qui esse videntur
                        in <placeName key="#Petiae #Houses #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Witness #Wood #Rent_in_kind #Operae #Exenia #Actionarii/actores #Wine #Minores #Legumes #Maiores #Hay/fodder #Fruits/vegetables #Land_clearing #Coloni/tenants" ref="#places/2492">Ostilia</placeName>, qui pertinet da parte
                        ipsius monesterii, in tantum in quantum ante os dies per temetipsum rectam
                        vel laboratam fuit, et iungo tibi medietatem de res illas in tantum in
                        quantum ante os dies per <persName><name ref="Sigismundus"
                            >Sexemundo</name></persName> rectam fuit, et medietatem de <rs
                            key="#Land_clearing">ronco</rs> illo qui per <persName><name
                                ref="Dominicus/Cianco">Domenico Cianco</name></persName> rectam fuit
                        qui <persName><name ref="Lanolus">Lanolo</name></persName> filio
                                <persName><name ref="Gisbertus">Gixeberti</name></persName>
                        ..3..adavit tam <rs key="#Petiae">sedimen</rs> cum <rs key="#Houses"
                            >caxa</rs>, curtem, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">orteo</rs>, areis, tam
                        teris, arvis et <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pradis</rs>, pascui, <rs key="#Wood"
                            >silvi</rs>, salecti adiciis vel <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">usum aquarum</rs> in
                        integrum. Ipsis rebus do tibi et ad tuis heredis ad lavorandum et super
                        resedere et lavorare et meliorare debeat sine fraudo vel nelicto, livellario
                        nomine, usque ad annis nomero viginti et nove. Et <rs key="#Rent_in_kind"
                            >reditum exinde persolvere</rs> repromito de ipsis rebus de omnium
                        laborem quem ibidem Dominus laborantibus dederit: de <rs key="#Maiores"
                            >maiorimen</rs> capa quarta in campo, de <rs key="#Minores">minudo</rs>
                        modio quinto in area, lino scuva quarta, et si <rs key="#Wine">vitis</rs>
                        posueritis redat porcionem quarta ad isto homnia <rs
                            key="#Actionarii/actores">miso domnico</rs> superadstantem. <rs
                            key="#Exenia">Esenio</rs> vero per omni anno dinarios octo et ipso
                        esenio datum et conpletum sit in misa sancti Martini. <rs key="#Operae"
                            >Operas</rs> vero per omni anno manibiles die sex et ipsas operas facere
                        debeat in Ostilia cum annona domnica; per tempore mesis vel vindimias miso
                        domnico cum onore susipiamus et sucepta faciamus; sic tamen ipso censo <rs
                            key="#Coloni/tenants">colonus</rs> cum suo dispengio vegere debeat usque
                        ad <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">cellam</rs> nostra <placeName key="#Rent_in_kind #Operae #Exenia #Actionarii/actores #Wine #Minores #Maiores #Legumes #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#places/1538"><geogName key="#Rent_in_kind #Operae #Exenia #Actionarii/actores #Wine #Minores #Maiores #Legumes #Cells/hermitages" ref="#estates/1111"
                            >Piscaria</geogName></placeName> et consigni nam alio nulllam. Ego
                        patrono vel mei suceptores te suprascripto colonus nec ad tuis heredis
                        nullam superimponere debeamus nisi qualiter superiuscriptum est. Pena vero
                        inter nobis stetit qui non conpleverit vel permanserit in eo homnia qualiter
                        superius legitur, et certe aparuerit veritas, tunc conponat pars ubi culpa
                        respeserit ad illa parte qui in sua fidem permanserit pena nomine solidos
                        duodicem et anc livello in sua maneat firmitatem. Duos livellos in uno
                        tinore scriptis ad omnia suprascripta. Acto in Ostilia, feliciter. Re
                        melioravimus ut de ortum et de rapas et <rs key="#Legumes">fasioli</rs> unde
                        non redatis. Signum (S) manus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Lupus"
                            >Luvoni</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name ref="Ursebertus"
                                >Ursepert</name></persName> da Ostilia <rs key="#Witness"
                                    >testi</rs>. Signum (S) manus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Ihoanni</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name ref="Dominicus"
                                >Domenico</name></persName> testis. Signum (S) manus <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Romanus">Romano</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Venerus">Venerio</name></persName> testi. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
